relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented, no acute distress (NAD)
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, moist mucous membranes
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/gallops/rubs (M/G/R)
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes/rales/rhonchi (W/R/R)
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, positive Murphy's sign, no rebound/guarding, focal tenderness to palpation (TTP) in the right upper quadrant (RUQ)
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused
